        <updateDate>2019-07-19T21:56:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ban Government Shutdowns Act </b></p> <p>This bill provides continuing appropriations to prevent a government shutdown if any appropriations measure has not been enacted before the beginning of the fiscal year or otherwise expires. </p> <p> The bill provides appropriations at the rate of operations that was provided for the prior fiscal year to continue programs, projects, and activities for which funds were provided in the preceding fiscal year.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
